data.description: Welcome to the very exclusive and gated community of Barton Creek Lakeside. This prestigious area features a 24-hour manned security guard and is home to some of the most beautiful real estate in Texas. This exquisite home is perched on a generous 30,000+ SQFT corner lot just across the street from Lake Travis. It’s incredible curb appeal and close proximity to the lake make this residence an opportunity that simply can't be missed.  Inside you’ll discover the tranquility of this charming home and a multitude of amenities to enrich your lifestyle. Residents here have access to the renowned Championship Arnold Palmer Golf Course, a private country club, tennis courts, a state-of-the-art fitness center, and Olympic-sized swimming pools. These amenities collectively create the perfect retreat for any potential buyer.  The home itself offers an expansive open floor plan, spanning an impressive 2,925 sqft, 3 generously sized bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. With high ceilings throughout, this residence exudes an airy and welcoming ambiance.   Outside you’ll experience an oasis of relaxation and entertainment. With the incredible patio area designed with a fireplace it makes it the ideal spot to host gatherings and entertaining all your guests.
